    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/2fb8709afaf09343119f36798af6ebf8.apng?t=1769383615\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/2fb8709afaf09343119f36798af6ebf8.poster.avif?t=1769383615\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"Story Header\" width=616 height=56 /></picture></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Amalia as she searches for her friend in a land afflicted by a noxious fog. The deeper she ventures, the further she unravels a force that threatens far more than just one life.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/ae2a39e18b30c35c4a30aba9a9607eaa.poster.avif?t=1769383615\" aria-label=\"Clip of two characters fighting against snakes\" width=400 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/ae2a39e18b30c35c4a30aba9a9607eaa.webm?t=1769383615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/ae2a39e18b30c35c4a30aba9a9607eaa.mp4?t=1769383615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/80de2dd7e44b460f7e8e2033d5ab141f.poster.avif?t=1769383615\" aria-label=\"Features Header\" width=616 height=56 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/80de2dd7e44b460f7e8e2033d5ab141f.webm?t=1769383615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Real-time combat</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Start battles as you approach enemies on the field</strong>. No random encounters, no turns — just real-time combat.</li><li><strong>Choose from cooldown-based skills</strong>. No magic points to manage; HP replenishes after battle if your party is in good spirits.</li><li><strong>Manipulate enemy focus (aggro)</strong>, encourage teammates, and master skill rotations in a system inspired by MMORPGs and action RPGs.</li><li><strong>Play with friends</strong> (couch co-op) for even more chaos.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plenty of character customization</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Select abilities and enhance them with augments</strong> — discoverable gems that change how skills behave.</li><li><strong>Learn passive abilities from equipment</strong>, such as combat-start buffs or bonuses when allies fall.</li><li><strong>Combine skills</strong> to create devastating combos.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/3060cbc90bad05bd2bdc954dc5175572.poster.avif?t=1769383615\" aria-label=\"Clip of a character traveling to a mansion in the snow\" width=400 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/3060cbc90bad05bd2bdc954dc5175572.webm?t=1769383615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/3060cbc90bad05bd2bdc954dc5175572.mp4?t=1769383615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A focus on fun</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>15–25 hour story</strong> focused on relationships in a fog-plagued world.</li><li><strong>Gameplay variety</strong>: minigames, puzzles, and quests; performance affects difficulty.</li><li><strong>Encouraged item usage</strong>; refill empty bottles in towns instead of hoarding.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/ca785acff4e7107ad322d879cff6938e.apng?t=1769383615\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101780/extras/ca785acff4e7107ad322d879cff6938e.poster.avif?t=1769383615\" class=\"bb_img\" alt=\"Team Header\" width=616 height=56 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This project was built over 20 years through multiple engines, story rewrites, and with the help of a patient, supportive community.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>zexyu</strong> - Story, engineering, graphics</li><li><strong>SaKo</strong> - Character portraits</li><li><strong>puking rabbit</strong> - Monster sprites</li><li><strong>Pipasdefranilla</strong> - Character sprites</li><li><strong>Brandon McKagan</strong> - Music</li></ul>",
